00:46:14.481 --> 00:46:15.857
Nothing much.

773
00:46:58.233 --> 00:46:59.817
All right. so. we gotta make sure

774
00:46:59.859 --> 00:47:01.528
that fucking asshole Zaccaro

775
00:47:01.569 --> 00:47:03.112
gets out of there in one piece.

776
00:47:03.154 --> 00:47:04.948
Right?

777
00:47:04.989 --> 00:47:06.282
And then...

778
00:47:07.408 --> 00:47:08.618
Jimmy...

779
00:47:10.620 --> 00:47:13.456
I'm gonna need you to put
a bullet in Flanagan's head.

780
00:47:15.875 --> 00:47:18.711
Sorry. He's gotta go.

781
00:47:38.314 --> 00:47:39.899
Mickey?

782
00:47:39.941 --> 00:47:42.527
Hey. Look. it's my Irish friends!

783
00:47:42.569 --> 00:47:44.445
Or maybe they're Italians.

784
00:47:44.487 --> 00:47:46.114
I can't fucking tell anymore.

785
00:47:46.155 --> 00:47:47.508
Sweeney. get me the fuck out of here.

786
00:47:47.532 --> 00:47:49.075
Hey. you shut the fuck up!

787
00:47:49.117 --> 00:47:51.494
Hey! Mickey. Mickey. relax. all right?

788
00:47:51.536 --> 00:47:53.496
We're just here to talk.

789
00:47:53.538 --> 00:47:55.790
So put down the gun and let's talk.

790
00:47:55.832 --> 00:47:58.209
Hey. Jimmy. you know
this dago offered me

791
00:47:58.251 --> 00:48:00.837
a hundred thousand bucks?

792
00:48:00.878 --> 00:48:02.505
That's a lotta money. right. Jimmy?

793
00:48:03.381 --> 00:48:05.091
- It sure is.
- What do you think?

794
00:48:05.133 --> 00:48:07.176
Should we take him up on it?

795
00:48:07.218 --> 00:48:08.761
- Sure.
- Yeah?

796
00:48:08.803 --> 00:48:10.638
- Yeah.
- Well. Davey O'Brien

797
00:48:10.680 --> 00:48:12.599
was only asking
for five grand. it turns out.

798
00:48:12.640 --> 00:48:14.392
You kill him over that. Mr. Sweeney?

799
00:48:16.603 --> 00:48:18.313
We're all friends here. Mickey.

800
00:48:19.981 --> 00:48:21.417
You know. I didn't believe this fucker

801
00:48:21.441 --> 00:48:23.276
when he first told me.

802
00:48:23.318 --> 00:48:25.486
but now I see that you're here
with your guns ready.

803
00:48:25.528 --> 00:48:27.780
I'm guessing it's true. fellas?

804
00:48:27.822 --> 00:48:30.033
Mickey. Mickey. look at me. look at me.

805
00:48:31.075 --> 00:48:32.910
It's me.

806
00:48:32.952 --> 00:48:35.204
We've been through a lot together. right?

807
00:48:36.372 --> 00:48:38.249
You know I'd never hurt you.

808
00:48:38.291 --> 00:48:40.251
but I am telling you.

809
00:48:40.293 --> 00:48:42.170
you have gotta let this guy go.

810
00:48:46.257 --> 00:48:47.759
You're on his side?

811
00:48:47.800 --> 00:48:49.236
For fuck's sake. Mickey.
I'm trying to help you.

812
00:48:49.260 --> 00:48:50.678
Eamon. kill this motherfucker now!

813
00:48:50.720 --> 00:48:52.114
- Shut the fuck up!
- Kill this motherfucker!

814
00:48:52.138 --> 00:48:54.932
Please. I am begging you!
Mickey. I am begging you.

815
00:48:54.974 --> 00:48:56.684
Just give me the fuckin' gun.

816
00:48:56.726 --> 00:48:58.561
You know what. Jimmy.

817
00:48:58.603 --> 00:49:01.022
I'm glad that you're here.

818
00:49:01.064 --> 00:49:02.565
'Cause you and I both know

819
00:49:02.607 --> 00:49:04.609
I'm not gettin' out of here alive.

820
00:49:04.651 --> 00:49:07.111
I'm just trying to decide
who I need to take with me.

821
00:49:07.153 --> 00:49:08.922
Now. look. no one's
gonna die here. all right?

822
00:49:08.946 --> 00:49:10.782
No one's gonna die.

823
00:49:10.823 --> 00:49:12.283
I think that you're wrong.

824
00:49:15.995 --> 00:49:17.372
You know what. Jimmy?

825
00:49:18.873 --> 00:49:20.458
I'll make it easy for ya.

826
00:49:26.631 --> 00:49:27.840
If it's gotta be done...

827
00:49:29.509 --> 00:49:31.219
I think you're the one that should do it.

828
00:49:31.260 --> 00:49:34.138
Thank fucking God.
Shoot this motherfucker.

829
00:49:34.180 --> 00:49:35.515
Kill this fucking kid.

830
00:49:36.641 --> 00:49:38.017
Come on.

831
00:49:39.143 --> 00:49:40.395
Go on. Jimmy.

832
00:49:42.063 --> 00:49:43.564
Truth is. brother...

833
00:49:44.941 --> 00:49:46.984
everybody is turning fucking orange...

834
00:49:49.487 --> 00:49:51.823
and I ain't got nothing except for you.

835
00:49:51.864 --> 00:49:54.867
So do it. Just fucking do it.

836
00:49:56.369 --> 00:49:57.870
Get it over with.

837
00:49:57.912 --> 00:49:59.622
These fucking dumb micks.

838
00:49:59.664 --> 00:50:01.666
they can't follow orders.
Do it yourself. Eamon.

839
00:50:01.708 --> 00:50:03.918
It's okay.

840
00:50:03.960 --> 00:50:05.503
I understand. Just do it.

841
00:50:07.630 --> 00:50:08.840
It's okay.

842
00:50:13.386 --> 00:50:14.929
I'm sorry. Eamon.

843
00:50:18.015 --> 00:50:19.475
Fuck it!

844
00:50:24.939 --> 00:50:27.650
Do you know the fuckin' trouble
you just caused us?

845
00:50:27.692 --> 00:50:29.652
We're Irish.

846
00:50:29.694 --> 00:50:31.529
We always got troubles.

847
